= A generic type for classes that receive string values as results =

The StringOperationListener type allows a class to declare that it is able to
receive a string value as a result of an operation.

= to_event_receiver =

Wrap this event listener object to a standard EventReceiver object. Any String
values will then be treated appropriately, and passed to the original object.

= on_string =

Called when an operation has a String to submit.

